<chapter xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0">
  <title>The config controller</title>
  <para>
    The <command>/config</command> context path allows you to apply a new configuration. The configuration is
    applied silently.
  </para>

  <sect1>
    <title>Type tag and parameters</title>
    <para>
      The type tag of the request looks like following: <parameter class="command">,s</parameter>.
    </para>

    <table border="1">
      <caption>Type tag description</caption>
      <thead>
	<tr>
	  <td>index</td>
	  <td>type indentifier</td>
          <td>value</td>
	</tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
	<tr>
	  <td>#0</td>
	  <td>s</td>
          <td>Your new configuration to apply</td>
	</tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </sect1>
    
</chapter>
